cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.LG, cs.CL. 

The paper deals with document image analysis, which involves computer vision techniques for processing images of documents. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves compression techniques, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.DL (Digital Libraries). The use of machine learning algorithms for text-line segmentation could also fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.CL (Computation and Language).
